headline: Truist Raises its Price Target on Vulcan Materials Company (VMC) to $360 and Maintains a Buy Rating
summary: Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE:VMC) is among the 10 High Growth S&P 500 Stocks to Buy Now. Truist on February 19, 2026, raised its price target on Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE:VMC) to $360 from $320 and maintained a Buy rating. The firm acknowledged a Q4 earnings miss but said the 2026 outlook still points to year-over-year […]
